thread.title: BobDylan

author: BobDylan
title: BobDylan
text: Refused to pay for aus post satchel, theres no other way of sending it, free printed postage, you print it out to attach to letters only, doesn't include satchels, which means you can't send it for free that way because smart phone doesn't fit inside an envelope, without being severely damaged. However to get free postage he must send prepaid satchel which you then must post wasting a week or more depending on your location. Not clear.
